{"tid":253131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓 朱古力 我屌你老母","createTime":"2017-05-22T06:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T13:20:31.000Z","uid":28510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48d068a7d93c8dd2cb19a8a5c91f14ea37fc9a8e","tid":253131,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"話說同事出cheap去左賓賓國 <br />\n帶左啲朱古力返來 <br />\n本來唔撚想食 但個個都食 連老細都食 之後唯有食<br />\n屌你老母 食完集體肚痛<br />\n依家個個爭廁所用 <br />\n好彩我醒目 一早霸住個屎坑<br />\n有條友係咁拍門<br />\n我無理鳩佢 最佢聽佢好痛苦又突然悉懷<br />\n既叫聲 我諗佢應該瀨咗<br />\n去屎坑成日 最後收工前我先出返來<br />\n照知比老闆照肺 問我之前係唔係廁格<br />\n我話 係<br />\n佢之後就叫我聽日唔洗返工<br />\n仆街 原來係出面瀨屎果個係佢 <br />\n屌你老母 賓賓朱古力 累我無左份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636a0cf4b9c125b4eb85826dc50dcd36f939fa43","tid":253131,"uid":41174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"0分重作"},{"pid":"4f333eb487834abbe6ecfe98c335fff02b177df4","tid":253131,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>0分重作</blockquote><br />\n真人真事"},{"pid":"2083c34ba7413fe707483ff83f61193cf3a7a761","tid":253131,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"依家仲未屙乾淨<br />\n個屎忽屙到開花<br />\n廁紙都用左幾桐"},{"pid":"a475b36f59271ed6d522c50b5f7ed0c404b99f14","tid":253131,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/22/151910_c08c35a2b953fcbc39d32f849e6a53de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2F151910_c08c35a2b953fcbc39d32f849e6a53de.jpg&h=b9246200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n認住呢件仆街朱古力 咪撚食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你便秘左成幾個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894b6535a1728a1cfffd49c9f65581bf1734ba38","tid":253131,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/22/152907_ea473a191e76c197b9f7fbb6bcc23387.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2F152907_ea473a191e76c197b9f7fbb6bcc23387.jpg&h=f18a1446&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d427e24552933439ebab7ed56afd5c3a450b4bd","tid":253131,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:16:06.000Z","msg":"仆街 又爆左兩次 屎眼都損晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddf200588d42a8d515bc24571addd0cd4e11b9e6","tid":253131,"uid":66546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:20:31.000Z","msg":"咩歌?"}]}